data.description: Location.. Location.. Location..  This property is very versatile...Currently used as a single family home with a large first floor living space featuring an expansive kitchen, separate laundry room, two baths, living room and possibility of three bedrooms.  Move upstairs and find two bedrooms, a full bathroom, kitchen, and flex room.  For even more room walk upstairs to the third floor to find two more rooms.  So many possibilities for this property it can be used as a single family residence or you can rent the second floor and live on the first to help offset the mortgage.  Another option if you have an in home business that is possible as well use part of the building for your business and live in the other part.  Building was once a doctors office so could be converted back to full commercial use with a large parking lot. Definitely a must see property to fully appreciate... Curious? Interested? Call today for more details or a private showing.  Open House Sunday November 19th 10:00-12:00.
